Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:16.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:20.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么到现在还要跟志愿生一起训练呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:24.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是为了做这种事而加入风纪委员的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:24.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:31.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  初春
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:33.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连一下都做不了么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:42.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不嫌弃的话  请用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:53.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…白井同学成为风纪委员已经一年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:53.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.19,0:00:57.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  也已经能活跃在现场当中了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:00.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:03.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  像我这样的人是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.22,0:01:05.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我笨手笨脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:08.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想着如果成为风纪委员的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:08.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:11.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样的我也说不定会有所改变才报名志愿的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:14.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全跟不上训练进度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:18.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵循自己坚信的正义
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:21.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采取正确的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:24.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是成为风纪委员的心得之一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:24.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.43,0:01:28.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有贯彻信念的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.47,0:01:30.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定会有成果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:05.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:09.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他需要设置的地方是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:11.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那里和那里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:17.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  到现在为止都不去增设监视摄像头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:22.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这所学校的风纪委员也够悠闲的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:22.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:25.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在受到损失之前意识到真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:27.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:29.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出动了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:30.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:40.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:42.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在光天化日之下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:43.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学校内
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:45.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是在风纪委员面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:45.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:47.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同学这样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:49.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在增援来之前请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:51.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:53.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春在这里待机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.41,0:03:57.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:01.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是风纪委员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:01.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:05.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以损害私人物品兼盗窃现行犯的罪名将你逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.29,0:04:05.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:07.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:08.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方可能不止一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:11.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有几个人  充其量也就是些砸车窗贼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:12.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下下就解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:16.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  给我放老实点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:19.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会为难…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:21.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:22.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  开溜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停…停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:27.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:35.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:42.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春  初春  振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:44.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:49.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:51.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:54.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我都折寿了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:57.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砸车窗贼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:58.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:00.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:04.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然初春还只是半吊子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:09.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟之前一样在支部负责我的后方支援就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.03,0:05:14.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…其实我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:18.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也说过对方可能不止一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:21.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无视这个的是白井同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:21.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:23.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来白井同学老是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:25.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爱乱来老是擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以检讨书才会有增无减的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:31.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这真是听不下去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:33.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候擅自行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:36.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么时候啊  什么时候都是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:38.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次也明明可以等增援来了再行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:41.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样优柔寡断的话就会给犯人逃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:43.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就稍微反省一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:47.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去我们的约定怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:53.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:56.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不记得…了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:58.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:04.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  既然白井同学这样想的话那我就不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:06.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:20.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:22.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:23.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:26.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  这里可不是休息室哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:28.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是  我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:30.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…今天有正当的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:36.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵！我的补习资料  想找初春帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:39.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  初春同学的话  看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:44.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在还是先别去的好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:46.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春同学情绪有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:48.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初～春～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:51.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  今天是三叶草小裤裤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:54.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  幸福的四叶草在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:57.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？喂喂  喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:00.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飘起来哦了  这可是绝景哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:05.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春她到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟白井同学发生了些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:09.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.38,0:07:15.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到这样的事情了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:17.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:20.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以稍微让她一个人静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:26.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么干脆别做风纪委员就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:26.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:30.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着慢着  别说这种没责任心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:36.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风纪委员可是跟警备员并行的学园都市治安维持机关哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:36.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(120,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:36.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:39.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是能够随便辞退的工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:43.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就这样放着她不管吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:46.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也不能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:48.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我想应该没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:51.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  她们两个有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:54.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想听吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:12.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…真是的  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:16.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊  那么在意的话就快点去和好不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:20.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:24.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话  初春说不定真的会讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:26.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除和你的组合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:30.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样就结束了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:34.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就说明我们间的感情不过如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:36.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又这样逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:37.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有逞强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:42.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和初春明明性格相差这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:44.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么组成组合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:48.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我其实也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:52.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初也没有这个打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:56.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那样迟钝又什么也做不到的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:57.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即便这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:06.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今天的巡逻就到这里结束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:09.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么在意的问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:13.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…稍微有点事情想问的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:14.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.91,0:09:17.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都当了一年的风纪委员了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.91,0:09:17.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(370,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:23.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么交给我的工作都是后勤和打杂  与前辈一起的巡逻而已呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:29.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对成绩优秀的自己却被当作半吊子看待觉得很不满吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:32.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是这个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:36.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是因为我还是个小学生才会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:40.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不单是年龄的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:43.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的情况是  拥有很大的潜能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:47.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却因此喜欢把所有事情都自己解决
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:51.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再稍微依靠一下身边的人会很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:54.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  别摆着这副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:58.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为帮了那么多忙的奖励  买些甜点给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去取些钱来  稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:04.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是把我当作小孩子看待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:18.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  白井同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:20.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:23.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春  为什么你会在第七学区里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:28.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快成为中学生了  我来看一下学校和宿舍的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:29.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学生？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:31.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:34.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:36.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌呢  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:37.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…哎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:39.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我同岁么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:41.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以为她比我小两三岁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:45.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同学已经决定了去哪间中学了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:49.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯  叫做常盘台中学的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:49.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:55.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起常盘台中学的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:59.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是在学园都市里都首屈一指的名门院校哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:03.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…学园生活也想必很优雅的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:07.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上也不尽是像那样美好的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:13.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不谙世事的有钱人  加上在校学生全部都是强能力者以上的能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:13.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(445,328)\fs18}Level 3
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:18.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集着一大帮把自己看得与众不同的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:24.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面还有叫做「超电磁炮」的超能力者的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:24.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,328)\fs18}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:24.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:28.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是个既傲慢又讨人厌性格恶劣的女人错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:33.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对素未谋面的人亏你能说成这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说回来你到邮局干什…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:37.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:38.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:41.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:49.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人光是在注意着邮局人员的位置和视线
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:50.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:56.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然随便看别人的私人物品有点过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:01.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不是带着什么奇怪的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:05.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右边口袋里面有手枪…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是强盗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去汇报情况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:11.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:12.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去做好将人群疏散的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:14.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不逮捕他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:16.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想着干傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:19.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人的逮捕工作就交给警备员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:19.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(410,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:24.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种消极的想法…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:27.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  请立即联系警备员…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:27.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(386,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:36.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别干什么奇怪的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:40.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客…客人们也安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:43.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  被抢先了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:45.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要像训练时那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:50.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:05.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀  小菜一碟嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:11.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  白痴啊  居然被一个小鬼给撂倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:12.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:14.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.53,0:13:18.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你们俩认识么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:22.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:26.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别轻举妄动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:27.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是风纪委员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:27.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:31.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的话应该不会弃人质于不顾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:34.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况是自己的朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里还有你的同伴在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:36.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:39.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要现身的话就趁现在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:49.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事  居然在这种时候鸣响警报
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:52.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道客人的生命还不及金钱来的重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:56.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接收防卫信号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:13:58.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始排除入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:01.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:01.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请缴械投降
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:02.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右边的口袋里放着什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.06,0:14:07.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告完毕  开始执行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:25.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:29.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:36.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在摸清对手底细之前  切忌轻举妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:39.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要铭记于心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:40.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:45.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:46.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:52.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为能像干掉那傻子一样干掉我么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:14:58.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:02.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:03.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:05.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:08.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:11.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我轻率的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:14.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连累了初春和固法前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:20.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这副狼狈样  这不是连半吊子都不如吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:23.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  浪费我的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.76,0:15:27.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:32.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有完没完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:35.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:40.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会…想办法把你救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:42.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又想玩什么把戏…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:49.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:51.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「空间移动」么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:51.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,328)\fs18}Teleport
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:55.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同学  你还在里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:56.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只把我给送出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:15:59.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢耍我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:01.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同学也请快逃出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:07.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想逃出去  可我还无法对自己使用能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:12.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  事件还没有解决呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:14.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:19.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人啊  求求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:20.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请帮帮我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:22.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面有强盗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:25.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风纪委员被强盗袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:25.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(260,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:28.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你们帮帮我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:31.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来猜猜看你在想什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:35.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警报也响了有一会儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:37.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警备员也差不多该就位了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:37.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(240,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:39.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要保证人质的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:42.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功地拖住我的话就是自己的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:44.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:50.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你怎么知道我一定无法从这里脱身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:01.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「绝对等速」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:01.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,328)\fs18}Equal Speed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:04.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所投掷出的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非其本身遭到破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:07.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是能力效果被解除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:09.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则无论前面出现什么都会继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:15.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是遗憾啊  让你白费了一番功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:19.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:23.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着  用你的能力把里面的钱转移出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:24.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你协助我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:26.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把所有人都放了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:30.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:32.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要和我合作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:34.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我联手的话可就天下无敌了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:35.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:39.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为第一次工作实在是太失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:44.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅擅自行动  还将大家都牵连进来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:46.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:51.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:55.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会与你为伍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:57.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让我帮你？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:18:03.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不巧  我对只知道袭击邮局的没出息的小贼连半点兴趣都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.95,0:18:04.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:07.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你们了  来人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:08.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经在此下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:13.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己所坚信的正义  决不会屈折
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:17.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么  真是遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:20.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种能力  空有力量却完全没有速度可言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:23.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要双腿能够听话的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:26.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你就死在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:30.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁说一次只能投掷一颗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:31.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:43.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.84,0:18:56.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的铁珠和我的空间移动究竟谁快  来一决高下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.84,0:18:56.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(284,328)\fs18}Teleport
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:01.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:03.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:05.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:28.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同学果然很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:31.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到你能够以一人之力将事件解决
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:35.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此宣誓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:45.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「遵循自己坚信的正义  采取正确的行动」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:50.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会将自己坚信的正义贯彻到底
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:52.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论遇到什么事都决不气馁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:56.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天  我也会成为像白井同学那样的风纪委员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:56.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(495,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:02.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的誓言  也请容许我借用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:07.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我一直以为可以凭一己之力解决任何事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:09.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:15.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  你愿意和我一起努力  成为独当一面的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:21.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:27.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多美好的回忆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:31.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:37.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来所谓的约定是指那件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:40.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  事到如今该怎么道歉才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:44.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是白井
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:46.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  初春她？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:48.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:51.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说之前的停车场盗窃犯的藏身之处已经确定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:52.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就突然飞奔出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:55.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子在那之后也一直在搜索哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:57.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  白井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:20:58.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:01.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:07.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「遵循自己坚信的正义  采取正确的行动」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:08.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:09.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:11.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕彼此发生些小摩擦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:14.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要事后仍能携手共进的话又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:32.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在磨蹭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:37.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话  要何时才能真正一起做到「独当一面」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.79,0:21:43.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会让人操心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:45.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:50.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不由得让人感到  那就是青春吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.26,0:21:54.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白…白井同学  你不觉得有点快过头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:21:56.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  要丢下你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:21:59.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用空间转移太不公平啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:21:59.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,328)\fs18}Teleport
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.29,0:23:32.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子和初春可真是青春激荡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.15,0:23:33.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风纪委员可不是三两下就能看透的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.15,0:23:33.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(200,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.86,0:23:35.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人是否也来体验一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.48,0:23:37.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  姐姐大人的初体验
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:37.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万别害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.85,0:23:39.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别乱扯！


